Friednly reminder for all the pool operators:

Komodo v0.5.0 (Obsidian Dragon) mandatory update is ready and available on GitHub : https://github.com/KomodoPlatform/komodo/tree/master - release: https://github.com/KomodoPlatform/komodo/releases/tag/0.5.0

Please update your Komodo infrastructure to this version as soon as possible.

The update goes live (activates) on December 20, at block 1,670,000.
